"WILL NOT DELETE OR MODIFY YOUR GAME FILES. TO DECREASE APPLICATION STARTUP "
"TIMES IT'S RECOMMENDED TO DELETE THE SYSTEM DIRECTORIES YOU DON'T NEED AFTER "
"RUNNING THIS UTILITY"
